_sText:
This is a huge remake from my old map 'deathrun_texture_extreme_v2'.
Only tested in CSS.

There's a lot of work in this map, you have to ❤️ it. If not, idc

Details
  1. 20 traps ☢️
  2. four t spawns
  3. 60 ct spawns
  4. five different endings to choose from
  5. eight digit hidden code
  6. four fancy nades ✨
  7. lots of great sounds
  8. minimap ✅

Bugs
There should be no bugs... but if there are (and there always are), please let me know!
